{"tid":636891,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插呀婆救教]Simple linear regression同multiple既問題","createTime":"2018-04-21T10:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T03:21:34.000Z","uid":67173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df8f838c0ebb34e7fce1618e960dc51ca9a71e25","tid":636891,"uid":67173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:14:26.000Z","msg":"份功課要set up model去用SPSS做<br />\n咁我地個model大致係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/180801_e7ea291ffb66864b24fdbc42e474e66d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F180801_e7ea291ffb66864b24fdbc42e474e66d.jpg&h=0905c8da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA B C D under同一個idea 但我地想各自分析對E有咩影響<br />\n所以我地做左linear regression先<br />\n結果都show到 H1到H4都係positively significant<br />\n<br />\n之後呀sir話做埋multiple去睇A B C D邊一個對E影響最大<br />\n姐係做multiple linear regression 做完之後<br />\n<br />\nH1係positively significant (p &lt; 0.01)<br />\n但H2,H3會變左negatively significant ( beta變左負數 )<br />\nH4直頭變左唔significant <br />\n<br />\n想問下點解H2,H3 同埋 H4會有咁既轉變 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n求下巴打們幫幫手"},{"pid":"a42cf081bbfd587ad27393a58cde42e4ade34bd1","tid":636891,"uid":67173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1618f24a176bd97e63381c4a827a9ab77daf6a07","tid":636891,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:51:46.000Z","msg":"你應該淨係H1 H2 H3再run多次multiple regression"},{"pid":"4468bda994d4b6b4d72f683c572627acd9806043","tid":636891,"uid":67173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1618f24a176bd97e63381c4a827a9ab77daf6a07","tid":636891,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:51:46.000Z","msg":"你應該淨係H1 H2 H3再run多次multiple regression"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"唔係好明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁姐係點"},{"pid":"bee713722d6edc267e64872c39ed7597a1829d83","tid":636891,"uid":67173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ac8270bd1d671bcc54168aa07627c292140824","tid":636891,"uid":180385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T20:24:59.000Z","msg":"Multicolinearity"},{"pid":"374965e7bb28c685f221920b0accea0e50dab88b","tid":636891,"uid":114447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T03:21:34.000Z","msg":"你整個h1-h4 correlation matrix 先"}]}